->creating of virtual env
syntax:-
-->pip install virtualenv
virtualenv virtualenvname

->install django
syntax:-
pip install django

->create one empty django project and application
syntax for creation of project

--> django-admin startproject projectname

syntax for creation of new application

--> pthon manage.py startapp application name
# manage.py is a script which is used to run administrative tasks like intialising the database running the development server and similar.
